"'''[[Permaéconomie]]'''" : French Book by Emmanuel Delannoy (October 2016)

'''*Source : http://www.wildproject.org/permaeconomie (in French)'''

=Description=

"Still obscured by the din of the old world, an economic revolution is underway. Based on a new relationship with the living, inspired by permaculture, the permaeconomy maintains the richness of the biosphere, the fundamental basis of all prosperity.

But in the current model, our economy no longer seems able to create shared prosperity that we are entitled to expect from it. The trust is gone. Whose fault is it ? It is of course the excesses of financialised capitalism "above ground" and a silent majority that is overwhelmed by a system whose workings escape them.

To seek to understand is already to disobey. To produce differently, to consume differently is already to resist. Revolutionary new models are already at work: circular economy, economics of functionality, Biomimicry ...

The permaeconomy is the new paradigm that allows them to be consistent. Emmanuel Delannoy presents here the principles and its first achievements for citizens, entrepreneurs, and decision makers."

